OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775311858
OL,3,CIran war leaving Australian farmers
OL,4,Cstruggling to sow crops and feed
OL,5,Canimals
OL,7,FThe three most vital supplies for
OL,8,Ffarmers in Australia are fuel,
OL,9,Ffertiliser and feed for the animals.
OL,10,FAt Jim Watt's dairy farm in
OL,11,FQueensland, he's running low on all
OL,12,Fthree.
OL,14,FHe's been forced to ration diesel, cut
OL,15,Fback on how many feeds he gives his
OL,16,Fcattle, and he can't afford
OL,17,Ffertiliser, so he hasn't sown his oat
OL,18,Fcrop for this season.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775311858
OL,3,CIran war leaving Australian farmers
OL,4,Cstruggling to sow crops and feed
OL,5,Canimals
OL,7,FHe would usually feed his cows every
OL,8,Fday of the week with a dry ration, but
OL,9,Flately he hasn't been doing that
OL,10,Fbecause of the diesel prices. But that
OL,11,Fhas had the knock-on effect of almost
OL,12,Fhalving his milk production, and his
OL,13,Fprofits.
OL,15,FAustralia is one of the biggest diesel
OL,16,Fconsumers in the world. The Iran war
OL,17,Fhas sent fuel costs to record highs
OL,18,Fand hundreds of petrol stations have
OL,19,Frun dry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
