CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775311858
OL,3,CIran war leaving Australian farmers
OL,4,Cstruggling to sow crops and feed
OL,5,Canimals
OL,7,FOn Thursday the Prime Minister
OL,8,Fannounced more emergency measures,
OL,9,Fincluding interest free loans for
OL,10,Fbusinesses involved in fuel,
OL,11,Ffertilizer and other critical supply
OL,12,Fchains. Antony Albanese said the
OL,13,Fnation was facing a testing time, with
OL,14,Fpetrol and diesel prices seeing their
OL,15,Fbiggest increase in history.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
