OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775311858
OL,3,CIran war leaving Australian farmers
OL,4,Cstruggling to sow crops and feed
OL,5,Canimals
OL,7,FHe said no government could "promise
OL,8,Fto eliminate" the impact of the
OL,9,Fconflicts in the Middle East, but he
OL,10,Fadded that measures like the loans
OL,11,Fwould act like a "shock absorber, in a
OL,12,Ftime of global shocks".
OL,14,FThe vast distances Australians often
OL,15,Fneed to travel to access shops and
OL,16,Fservices is why this fuel crisis is
OL,17,Fbiting so hard, particularly for the
OL,18,Fisolated and vulnerable.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
