OL,3,CIran war leaving Australian farmers
OL,4,Cstruggling to sow crops and feed
OL,5,Canimals
OL,7,FAt TransitCare, they are trying to
OL,8,Fcontinue their support for tens of
OL,9,Fthousands of elderly and disabled.
OL,10,FThey provide transport for those who
OL,11,Faren't so mobile and those can't
OL,12,Faccess public transport or afford it.
OL,14,FAs a charity their margins are already
OL,15,Fthin, and the fuel price rises have
OL,16,Fhad a devastating effect.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
