OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775311858
OL,3,CIran war leaving Australian farmers
OL,4,Cstruggling to sow crops and feed
OL,5,Canimals
OL,7,FThe CEO Amanda Mather told us that
OL,8,Fthey are facing an increase of more
OL,9,Fthan $45,000 a month in fuel prices
OL,10,Falone, enough to send the company into
OL,11,Fthe red by the end of this financial
OL,12,Fyear.
OL,14,FOne fuel industry potentially set to
OL,15,Fgain, is coal. Production in Australia
OL,16,Fhas been ramped up, to help South
OL,17,FKorea and Japan who are facing major
OL,18,Fgas shortages.
OL,20,FIt's an emergency fix, which could set
OL,21,Fback the regions' climate targets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
