OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775311858
OL,3,CIran war leaving Australian farmers
OL,4,Cstruggling to sow crops and feed
OL,5,Canimals
OL,7,FFor Jim saving his farm is the
OL,8,Fpriority, he was hoping his son would
OL,9,Fbe the fourth generation to take it on.
OL,11,FHe predicts there will be empty
OL,12,Fshelves in the supermarkets in the
OL,13,Fcoming weeks, and he's worried he
OL,14,Fwon't be able to sustain a living on
OL,15,Fthe farm.
OL,17,FHe knows from too much experience that
OL,18,Fthis is critical time for his family
OL,19,Fbusiness.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
